public abstract class chipCell<FINALTYPE extends chipCell<FINALTYPE,COMPONENTTYPE>,COMPONENTTYPE extends chip>
extends cell<FINALTYPE>

this is the principal subclass of cell for cells whose contents is just a single object. The methods here are designed to be compatible with those of stackCell so the same coding idioms can be used for both.

Author:
ddyer
See Also:
